Description: Sovereign Edge Model Operating System
 Cell 0 OS is a multi-layer computational substrate that combines
 a bare-metal kernel, AI inference engine, and user interface layers
 into a unified sovereign operating system.
 .
 Features:
  - Edge-optimized AI inference (Ollama, MLX)
  - Multi-agent coordination system
  - Sovereign TPV (Thought-Preference-Value) profiles
  - Web UI, CLI, and REST API interfaces
  - Prometheus metrics and Grafana dashboards
  - Kubernetes and Docker deployment ready
